<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">Print a booklet on a double-sided printer</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">You can make a folded booklet (like a small book or pamphlet) by printing
  pages of a document in a special order and changing a couple of printing
  options.</p>
<p class="p">将 PDF 文档打印成册的指导说明。</p>
<p class="p">如果您是从 <span class="app">LibreOffice</span> 文档打印小册子，首先要导出为 PDF 文档，点菜单<span class="guiseq"><span class="gui">文件</span> ▸ <span class="gui">导出为 PDF…</span></span>，确保文档有4倍以上页面的内容(4,、8,、12、16...)。您可能要添加上三页空白页。</p>
<p class="p">打印一本小册子：</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Open the print dialog. This can normally be done through
      <span class="gui">Print</span> in the menu or using the
      <span class="keyseq"><span class="key"><kbd>Ctrl</kbd></span>+<span class="key"><kbd>P</kbd></span></span> keyboard shortcut.</p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">Click the <span class="gui">Properties…</span> button </p>
<p class="p">In the <span class="gui">Orientation</span> drop-down list, make sure that
      <span class="gui">Landscape</span> is selected.</p>
<p class="p">In the <span class="gui">Duplex</span> drop-down list, select <span class="gui">Short Edge</span>.
      </p>
<p class="p">Click <span class="gui">OK</span> to go back to the print dialog.</p>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Under <span class="gui">Range and Copies</span>, choose <span class="gui">Pages</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">按下面的顺序输入页数(n 表示总的页数，应当是4的倍数)：</p>
<p class="p">n, 1, 2, n-1, n-2, 3, 4, n-3, n-4, 5, 6, n-5, n-6, 7, 8, n-7, n-8, 9, 10, n-9, n-10, 11, 12, n-11…</p>
<p class="p">例如：</p>
<div class="list"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul class="list">
<li class="list"><p class="p">4页小册子：输入 <span class="input">4,1,2,3</span></p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">8页小册子：输入 <span class="input">8,1,2,7,6,3,4,5</span></p></li>
<li class="list"><p class="p">20页小册子：输入 <span class="input">20,1,2,19,18,3,4,17,16,5,6,15,14,7,8,13,12,9,10,11</span></p></li>
</ul></div></div></div>
</li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">Choose the <span class="gui">Page Layout</span> tab.</p>
<p class="p">Under <span class="gui">Layout</span>, select <span class="gui">Brochure</span>.</p>
<p class="p">Under <span class="gui">Page Sides</span>, in the <span class="gui">Include</span> drop-down list,
      select <span class="gui">All pages</span>.</p>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">打印</span>按钮。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
</div>
